Additionally, I would suggest that "max" value is set to Long.MAX_VALUE. With this choice of "allow all" value branching will look like:
final long cursorSize = baseCursor.size();
if (cursorSize < maxInMemoryRows) {
// do the good stuff
} else {
      throw ....
